                  "title": "Empathy: \"It's time... to become a citizen of...\"",
                  "articyId": "0x01000045000207D5",
                  "text": "It's time... to become a citizen of the *Kingdom of Conscience*.",
                  "links": [
                    {
                      "id": 29,
                      "title": "You: \"First, where is this Kingdom of Con...\"",
                      "articyId": "0x01000045000207E4",
                      "text": "First, where is this Kingdom of Conscience?",
                      "links": [
                        {
                          "id": 48,
