                                                      "id": 32,
                                                      "title": "Empathy: \"You may never live to see the Kingd...\"",
                                                      "articyId": "0x0100009400000B70",
                                                      "text": "You may never live to see the Kingdom of Conscience. Your children may not. Even your *grandchildren* might not. But that's no excuse not to keep working...",
                                                      "links": [
                                                        {
                                                          "id": 58,
                                                          "title": "Logic: \"What rationality...\"",
