                                                                          "title": "Empathy: \"That's right. Remember -- *real dem...\"",
                                                                          "articyId": "0x0100009400000C15",
                                                                          "text": "That's right. Remember -- *real democracy* is just around the corner for Revachol. When that real democracy kicks in -- a long time from now -- we are all going to be so much happier.",
